# Amazigh Lineage Heritage - Site Design System & Style Guide

## Project Overview
This is a scientific research website documenting Amazigh (Berber) genetic heritage, specifically the Chtouka lineage from Souss-Massa, Morocco. The site combines genetics, history, anthropology, and cultural studies.

