## üéØ SEO PATTERNS

### Title Tags
- Length: 40-50 characters (optimized for better display)
- Format: "Primary Keyword | Secondary Keyword"
- Include main topic and location when relevant
- Example: "Amazigh DNA Heritage | E-PF2546 & H1 Research"

### Meta Descriptions
- Length: 150-160 characters
- Include primary keywords naturally
- End with call-to-action when possible
- Example: "Genetic analysis of Amazigh Chtouka lineage: E-PF2546 Y-DNA (400 BCE) and H1 mtDNA (10,000 years) from Souss-Massa, Morocco."

### Structured Data
- Always include JSON-LD schema
- Use appropriate types: WebSite, Article, ScholarlyArticle, FAQPage
- Include datePublished and dateModified
- Add FAQ schema for common questions

### Image SEO
- Descriptive alt text with keywords
- Include context and location
- Format: "Subject - Description - Location/Context"
- Example: "DNA helix visualization showing genetic heritage analysis of Amazigh Chtouka lineage from Souss-Massa, Morocco"

